# OBJECT::SET_OBJECT_TARGETTABLE

## Summary
The player can auto target the object

## Parameters
* **OBJECT_INDEX** objectID
* **BOOL** targettable

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Only four objects can be targettable at any time.
